<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="687" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="20.[828,1441,842,1121]" pageId="20" pageNumber="687">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[828,942,874,897]" pageId="20" pageNumber="687">Remarks.</emphasis>
The species was described generally from 
<collectingCountry box="[828,895,906,929]" name="Brazil" pageId="20" pageNumber="687">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(Bൺඅඒ 1859) and subsequently listed only in catalogues (e.g., UΗආൺඇඇ 1957). The only record so far was published by Bඈඇൽൺඋ (1938) from 
<collectingRegion box="[1216,1279,970,993]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="20" pageNumber="687">Bahia</collectingRegion>
but it was not mentioned in species distribution in the recent revision (Sඍൺංඇൾඌ +| Gൺඋർටൺ-Rඈൻඅൾൽඈ 2014). The species is here newly recorded from 
<collectingRegion box="[1069,1180,1066,1089]" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="20" pageNumber="687">São Paulo</collectingRegion>
and very likely occurs in all east Brazilian states.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
